{"id": 1058, "genre": 1001, "title": "什么样的好意会让你感到尴尬？", "description": "我知道你人美心善，但事情可能不是你想的那样......（题图来自：Patrizio Anastasi）", "record_count": 4214, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703181409xGtyTCvLRUcXQmZI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-17T11:01:58Z", "options": [{"id": 89856, "content": "很忙的时候邀我出去玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649225}, {"id": 90112, "content": "被男生提醒姨妈弄到裤子上了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649752}, {"id": 89601, "content": "春节回家全程。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346805}, {"id": 89857, "content": "每次被说：“哇！你好瘦！”或者“你那么瘦多吃点！”（内心其实想说，我真的吃很多。我也很想长胖的~）", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 557589}, {"id": 89858, "content": "认真指出一些无关紧要的问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649225}, {"id": 90114, "content": "丑女的殷勤！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525112}, {"id": 90370, "content": "饭桌上别人夹到不喜欢的菜放进自己碗里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648352}, {"id": 95490, "content": "上司给你加班饭的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667881}, {"id": 89603, "content": "你现在不结婚老了可怎么办？呵呵哒，宝宝老了自己把自己扛上六楼", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 351886}, {"id": 89859, "content": "毫无意义的附和", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649225}, {"id": 90883, "content": "多大了？大学毕业了咯！该找男朋友了！balabalabala", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495293}, {"id": 89604, "content": "说话总是慢一拍!等你开口的时候己经散场了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648148}, {"id": 89860, "content": "让我笑一笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488981}, {"id": 90372, "content": "啊哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648352}, {"id": 89606, "content": "帮我介绍女朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593531}, {"id": 89607, "content": "「给你介绍个女朋友哈」", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 71}, {"id": 89609, "content": "不喜欢看的演出硬是觉得你会喜欢买票给你", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648568}, {"id": 89865, "content": "正在试衣间里试衣服，然后导购姐姐就拿了几件衣服过来让我试试?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647367}, {"id": 89610, "content": "和亲戚一起吃饭给你夹了许多菜 还有你不喜欢的。可是尊敬长辈还是要吃下去?", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648591}, {"id": 89611, "content": "路边遇到派发减肥健身的课程优惠卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645950}, {"id": 90891, "content": "屈臣氏热情的BA", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651629}, {"id": 89612, "content": "超市促销阿姨~", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258093}, {"id": 90124, "content": "‍强加给的 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649769}, {"id": 89615, "content": "被递烟，被倒酒……但是我不烟不酒……", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154739}, {"id": 89616, "content": "说了再见却发现顺路", "image": null, "praise_count": 208, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647561}, {"id": 89618, "content": "所有商场热情的导购", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458087}, {"id": 89619, "content": "我妈发短信让我不要吃避孕药", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419850}, {"id": 89621, "content": "介绍相亲", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 441347}, {"id": 89877, "content": "我不方便的时候帮我收信件或者快递，但是拆开看。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 622297}, {"id": 89623, "content": "我来帮你洗碗吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 604937}, {"id": 90135, "content": "吃饭一直被长辈夹菜 特别有时候还会是自己不喜欢吃的菜", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649789}, {"id": 89625, "content": "肚子有点大容易被让坐", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648622}, {"id": 92697, "content": "介绍对象", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657007}, {"id": 89626, "content": "地铁被当做孕妇被让座，然而只是肚子肉多而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270249}, {"id": 89882, "content": "去买东西。回来却发现多了几个人，是吃还是不吃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649279}, {"id": 89627, "content": "他咬我的时候", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182720mxuq6184vjgpNoME.jpg", "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507360}, {"id": 90141, "content": "你这么黑，脸红的时候会被人发现么。如果能被发现，那只能说明别人眼力好。   我就是那个黑人，这么说我，真的好么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649792}, {"id": 90143, "content": "吃西红柿或者雪糕……吃着吃着 想起了你 ～快给你咬一口?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649793}, {"id": 91170, "content": "我觉得你胖了？（带疑问的认真脸）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652516}, {"id": 99618, "content": "明明是她的问题反而来提醒我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683498}, {"id": 89636, "content": "约我去玩我说没钱不去，她说我给你借…", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642904}, {"id": 89637, "content": "闺蜜妈妈要给我介绍对象", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633248}, {"id": 89638, "content": "好久不见老同学，我翻到了一张你 N 年前的老照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 186884}, {"id": 89639, "content": "好文", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450371}, {"id": 89642, "content": "你有眼屎／你裤子拉链开了／你假睫毛掉了", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 648669}, {"id": 90410, "content": "小林，阿姨再给你盛点饭。哪是一点，明明又是满满的一碗～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650371}, {"id": 89643, "content": "你牙好黄啊，去刷刷吧…(ㅍ_ㅍ)", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 567787}, {"id": 90155, "content": "你裤子湿了我借你一条吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649800}, {"id": 90667, "content": "介绍男朋友。。明明我还在读书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650979}, {"id": 89645, "content": "多吃点！胖点好…总是让我又哭又笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593360}]}